DummyEntityPersister - Class in org.grails.datastore.gorm.neo4j
dummy implementation of org.grails.datastore.mapping.engine.EntityPersister The Neo4j gorm implementation does all persistence stuff in Neo4jSession, so there's no need for a org.grails.datastore.mapping.engine.EntityPersister, except on issue: org.grails.datastore.gorm.proxy.GroovyProxyFactory references org.grails.datastore.mapping.engine.EntityPersister#setObjectIdentifier so Neo4jSession.proxy needs to pass a valid EntityPersister - that's the purpose of this class.
